black.content: Whenever the cashier at the grocery store asks my dad if he would like the milk in a bag he replies, _
What do you call Scooby Doo with a blunt in his mouth? _
Did you hear about the guy who invented Lifesavers? _
Me: Dad, make me a sandwich _
What time did the man go to the dentist? _
Why do chicken coops only have two doors? _
A ham sandwich walks into a bar and orders a beer. Bartender says, _
Why did the Clydesdale give the pony a glass of water? _

white: They say he made a mint.
No, just leave it in the carton.
Because he was a little horse.
Sorry we don't serve food here.
Because if they had four, they would be chicken sedans.
